<!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
<header class="pp-hero">
  <div class="container pp-hero__grid">
    <div class="pp-hero__copy">
      <span class="pp-badge"><i data-feather="shield"></i> Privacy First</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        FileMakr is built for <strong>academic use</strong>. We help students create and access
        <strong>project files, reports, and source code</strong>. We <strong>do not sell</strong> personal data. This page explains what we collect, why, and how we protect it.
      </p>
      <ul class="pp-hero__pills">
        <li><i data-feather="check-circle"></i> Academic purpose only</li>
        <li><i data-feather="lock"></i> Secure checkout</li>
        <li><i data-feather="user-check"></i> Your data, your control</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pp-hero__art" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="art-pro">
        <div class="art-pro__plate"></div>
        <div class="art-pro__ring art-pro__ring--a"></div>
        <div class="art-pro__ring art-pro__ring--b"></div>
        <div class="art-pro__grid"></div>
        <div class="art-pro__badge art-pro__badge--primary"><i data-feather="file-text"></i><span>Student-friendly</span></div>
        <div class="art-pro__badge art-pro__badge--accent"><i data-feather="lock"></i><span>Protected</span></div>
        <div class="art-pro__badge art-pro__badge--neutral"><i data-feather="zap"></i><span>Fast</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="pp-main">
  <!-- ===== Key Summary ===== -->
  <section class="pp-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pp-cards">
        <article class="pp-card">
          <i class="pp-ico" data-feather="info"></i>
          <h3>Who we are</h3>
          <p>FileMakr provides academic project files, reports, and source code for college students. Our services are strictly for <strong>learning and submission purposes</strong>.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="pp-card">
          <i class="pp-ico" data-feather="eye-off"></i>
          <h3>No data sales</h3>
          <p>We <strong>never sell</strong> personal data. Limited data is used to deliver orders, support, payments, and site analytics.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="pp-card">
          <i class="pp-ico" data-feather="server"></i>
          <h3>Minimal retention</h3>
          <p>We keep data only as long as necessary for <strong>orders, support, and legal obligations</strong>, then securely delete it.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Policy Body ===== -->
  <section class="pp-section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pp-body">
        <h2>Our commitment</h2>
        <p>
          Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how FileMakr (“we”, “us”) handles information on
          <a href="https://www.filemakr.com" rel="noopener">filemakr.com</a> and any related pages. By using our website, you agree to this policy.
        </p>

        <h3><i data-feather="clipboard"></i> What we collect</h3>
        <ul class="pp-list">
          <li><strong>Contact details</strong> (name, email, phone) to deliver downloads, receipts, and support.</li>
          <li><strong>Order data</strong> (items purchased, amounts, transaction IDs) to fulfill and support your order.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical data</strong> (device, browser, approximate location) via cookies/analytics to improve performance.</li>
          <li><strong>Support messages</strong> (email/WhatsApp/chat) to resolve queries quickly.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3><i data-feather="target"></i> Why we collect it</h3>
        <ul class="pp-list">
          <li>To <strong>process payments</strong> and deliver digital downloads.</li>
          <li>To provide <strong>customer support</strong> and optional code setup assistance.</li>
          <li>To <strong>improve the site</strong> (usage analytics and performance insights).</li>
          <li>To meet <strong>legal/accounting</strong> obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3><i data-feather="share-2"></i> Who we share it with</h3>
        <p>We don’t sell your data. Limited sharing happens with:</p>
        <ul class="pp-list">
          <li><strong>Payment processors</strong> (to complete transactions securely).</li>
          <li><strong>Cloud/hosting & analytics providers</strong> (to run our site and understand usage).</li>
          <li><strong>Messaging providers</strong> (WhatsApp/email) when you request support.</li>
          <li><strong>Law enforcement</strong> if required by law.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3><i data-feather="clock"></i> Data retention</h3>
        <p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to provide services and comply with legal obligations. After that, we <strong>delete or anonymize</strong> it.</p>

        <h3><i data-feather="cookie"></i> Cookies</h3>
        <p>We use essential cookies for website functionality and limited analytics cookies to improve performance. You can control cookies via your browser settings. Disabling some may affect site features.</p>

        <h3><i data-feather="shield"></i> Security</h3>
        <p>We use commercially reasonable safeguards (encryption in transit, access controls, hardened hosting) to protect data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

        <h3><i data-feather="external-link"></i> Third-party links</h3>
        <p>Our site may link to external websites. We don’t control their content or policies. Review their privacy policies for details.</p>

        <h3><i data-feather="user-x"></i> Children’s privacy</h3>
        <p>FileMakr is intended for college students. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you believe a child provided data, contact us to remove it.</p>

        <h3><i data-feather="edit-2"></i> Your choices & rights</h3>
        <ul class="pp-list">
          <li>Access, update, or delete your information (subject to legal retention).</li>
          <li>Opt out of non-essential emails (order-critical emails still apply).</li>
          <li>Control cookies in your browser.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3><i data-feather="message-circle"></i> Contact us</h3>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Need to exercise your rights?
          <br>
          Email/Chat: <a href="https://wa.me/918319339945" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp Support</a>
          or use our <a href="/contact-us">Contact form</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="pp-meta">
          <span><i data-feather="calendar"></i> Last updated:
            <%= (new Date()).toLocaleDateString() %></span>
          <span>Effective since: 18 November 2019</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="pp-cta">
    <div class="container pp-cta__box">
      <div>
        <h2>Built for students. Privacy by design.</h2>
        <p>Explore project files & source code for academic use — fast, secure, and student-friendly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pp-cta__actions">
        <a class="btn btn-brand" href="/final-year-project-ideas">Browse Project Files</a>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="https://wa.me/918319339945" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

